c: 31
v: 32
t: "Ke kaloku athi amaza esakubagquma okwamaphahla, bathandaze kuAllâh, benyanisekile kuYe enkolweni. Kodwa Esakubahlangulela emhlabeni kubakho abanye kubo abadikidiki (abaphakathi kokukholwa nokungakholwa). Ukanti akukho bani uzalayo iiVesi zeThu ngaphandle kwalowo unobungcatshi ongenambulelo"